# Info

Invoked every client tick (20 times per second).

>>> warning
This event fires very frequently. Be careful with performance-heavy operations!
<<<

# Available Event Fields

- `event.player` - The client player
- `event.level` - The level the player is in

# Example

```js
ClientEvents.tick(event => {
	// Only run every second (20 ticks)
	if (event.player.age % 20 !== 0) return
	
	// Do something every second
})
```
